  <brief_title>An Examination of the Safety and Blood Pressure Lowering Effect of Increasing Doses of Benicar速 and Benicar速 HCT in Patients With Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Open Label, Titration Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of Benicar速 and Benicar 速HCT in Patients With Stage II Systolic Hypertension</official_title>
